title: Dublin Food Co-op
description: Member-owned co-operative providing a selection of vegetarian, fair trade, and GMO-free organic wholefoods plus eco-friendly hygiene and cleaning products. On Saturday there are local growers and artisans trading food and crafts. On Sunday a monthly rotation of flea, vintage, brocante, and world fusion markets. Cafe closes at Fri 6:30pm shop 8pm.
